<span class="person">Peter Hickey</span> enjoys making sense of data 
and making it easier for others to do the same. He holds a PhD in 
Statistics and develops methods and software to summarise and understand 
genomics data. He especially loves the R programming language and the 
Bioconductor open-source community. </p>
